description: The Baker-Polito Administration announced a three-week suspension of school operations for educational purposes at all public and private elementary and secondary (K-12) schools in Massachusetts, USA, beginning Tuesday, March 17 2020.
type_sub_cat: Primary Schools (generally for children ages 10 and below)
